      White Papers
    %div{class: "product-detail__body text--link-list"}
      %ul
        %li{class: "alpha"}
          %a{href: "#white-paper"}
            %div{class: "text--link-list__arrow product-detail__arrow"} >          
            Nunc laoreet dignissim nisl, eu gravida eros congue ac, and you won't believe what happens next.
